Fixed HASerializedSessionExternalizer to correctly work with Infinispan.

Infinispan expect to know how to serialize a class or an Externalizer to be registered,
that was not the case for ConcurrentLinkedQueue class that was simplistically serialized with:
output.writeObject( object.buffer );
